data.name: textBox1.Value
data.value: The rates for Special Business Tax and Stamp Duty may change subject to Government regulations. Stamp Duty is charged on the annual amount and so if you pay quarterly subsequent payments will be reduced accordingly.

data.name: textBox19.Value
data.value: If you elect to pay by bank transfer, please ask your bank to advise your name and membership number to enable us to identify your payment. Please sign below to confirm your acceptance of the above terms and return it to us by fax on + 66 2 654 1151
